FoxTrick is a browser extension for the Hattrick online football manager
game, currently available for Mozilla-based browsers including Firefox, and
Google Chrome.

FoxTrick enhances the user experience on Hattrick by providing tons of extra
information, a lot of shortcuts, tweaks for the presentational layout of the
web pages, analyses of matches, links to utilities on external sites, and
provide browser-side alerts and notifications.

Homepage: http://code.google.com/p/foxtrick/
